<help skills construct>

Construct is a skill that allows one to build objects from other,
simpler components.  You cannot mess with components of a higher
level than yourself, so as you advance in level you will be able
to create greater and greater things! 

Syntax:  construct
<color=red>
See Also:  concoct, examine, put, get
</color>
Note:  You must have a toolbox in which to put your component parts.
</help>
